{"tid":232421,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"迪麗熱巴 Angelababy 邊個正啲","createTime":"2017-05-06T17:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T08:18:52.000Z","uid":101402,"like":97,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3e0ab2bb0304d436a88110df99b68ff06ee700d","tid":232421,"uid":101402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"迪麗熱巴，1992年6月3日出生於新疆烏魯木齊，中國內地女演員。<br />\n代表作品: 古劍奇譚，克拉戀人，漂亮的李慧珍，三生三世十里桃花。<br />\n迪麗熱巴是維吾爾族人，長着一看就知道是少數民族的那種長相，充滿了異域風情。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/oynyolo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Foynyolo.html&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=6f302103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/oynyolo.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBMi64p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBMi64p.jpg&h=ec3092ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Lc4XF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Lc4XF5.jpg&h=2c84f4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/010907_3c259411f879aa448d894e222c1a689a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F010907_3c259411f879aa448d894e222c1a689a.jpg&h=66fc73f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊穎Angelababy，1989年2月28日出生於上海市，華語影視女演員，時尚模特。<br />\n代表作品: 第一次，狄仁傑之神都龍王，微微一笑很傾城。<br />\nAngelababy的爺爺是德國人，所以擁有四分之一的德國血統<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/011312_cdba63b796b28659c59936429eb82e82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F011312_cdba63b796b28659c59936429eb82e82.jpg&h=60090d94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSGN2q1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSGN2q1.jpg&h=104169df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/011314_9f9e4ef446e98762beb2652d1f4c26ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F011314_9f9e4ef446e98762beb2652d1f4c26ef.jpg&h=06d0ae50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從迪麗熱巴代替Angelababy上咗跑男之後(因為baby要生baby)，關於倆人之間既爭鬥傳聞越來越厲害。兩個都喺奔跑吧固定女主持人，中意邊個多啲？<br />\n<br />\n正評: 迪麗熱巴<br />\n負評: Angelababy"},{"pid":"9508b3576efc00bed7d3f453f6537bcbe75e6a9d","tid":232421,"uid":99773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"baby無敵"},{"pid":"02e3a38d5a77b3c95845fa8616f402683c678da8","tid":232421,"uid":89270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:33:17.000Z","msg":"熱巴 小鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c1bd58ff0d92837421353b2ee9f41a98f8281d","tid":232421,"uid":19967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你</span></span>"},{"pid":"117dc49548ef7f6ca14adccc13b7142bbdc17039","tid":232421,"uid":67551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:44:21.000Z","msg":"梗係新疆妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35001ed16e86727962b8d9e0034971f6ad42efe","tid":232421,"uid":91096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:11:37.000Z","msg":"熱巴幾靚"},{"pid":"9efdbcd74b27320556883fb123a503dafe77a618","tid":232421,"uid":45471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"俄妹樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42550d81349dd9188bf337da3b17489b969ca7ca","tid":232421,"uid":37005,"like":2,"dislik